        <li>to protect our rights, company property, and safety of other company employees; and</li>
        <li>where otherwise required by law.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Sharing of Personal Information</h2>

      <p>Hanyu discloses Your Personal Information in limited circumstances to Hanyu's affiliates, our service providers, in order to provide our Hanyu Services and to improve your experience. Where required by applicable law, Hanyu will only share Your Personal Information for this very limited purpose.</p>

